{"tid":1306587,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"郭明錤：2021 年Touch ID 取代 Face ID， M 字額全面消失","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:46.000Z","uid":159066,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4e97064053bcfd08ba3b9ddb24d43a4ff63a02","tid":1306587,"uid":159066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/213518/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F213518%2F1%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt8526wVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=37cd187f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/213518/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n2019 年的新 iPhone 還未發表，網絡<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>已經有 2020 年的 iPhone 消息流傳，全因為經常準確預測 Apple 新產品動向的著名分析師郭明錤。他最近撰寫的報告中預測，明年發表的新 iPhone 機身設計會有大幅改變，而且 Touch ID 有望捲土重來，甚至會取代現時的 Face ID。<br />\n<br />\nApple 分析師爆料  新版 Touch ID 將取代 Face ID<br />\n<br />\nApple 會在明年全面更新 iPhone 產品線，預計 5.4 吋、6.1 吋和 6.7 吋型號都會使用 OLED 屏幕面板。此外，Apple 還會推出一款配備 Touch ID 功能的新款 iPhone，主力在中國大陸市場發售。雖然 Touch ID 鹹魚翻生，這並不代表實體 Home 鍵重新出現，而是採用現時 Android 手機普遍採用的屏幕指紋辨識技術。郭明錤指 2020 年至少一款 iPhone 屏幕的 M 字額範圍有望縮小，令屏佔比有所提升，這可能是 Apple 於這款 iPhone 取消 Face ID 使用的 TrueDepth 感應器所致。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報告又提到，Apple 打算在 2021 年發表的 3 款 iPhone，都會以 Touch ID 取代 Face ID，屆時 M 字額將會全面消失。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4720d61a4f847f411440ce162069764e185aca95","tid":1306587,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"front cam 點擺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08e6fb570dcc81932a135f5ca3dc92481e25eae","tid":1306587,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4720d61a4f847f411440ce162069764e185aca95","tid":1306587,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:10:00.